data.description: 100% USDA financing eligible for qualified purchaser! Nicely updated four bedroom home in Harvest Hills! Open floorplan boasts luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout the first floor. Updated kitchen features painted cabinetry, Corian countertops, and stainless steel appliances. Charming brick fireplace in first floor living room with walkout to deck. The second floor features four bedrooms including the primary suite with large bathroom and walk in closet. Finished lower level is fantastic for entertaining or guests with bonus room, large family room, half bathroom, and walkout to very private rear yard. Schedule your private showing today!
